message:
Version 0.6.0:
- New settings for the visualization of the home. Were added to two visualization modes (Classic: quick and easy; Advanced: with display pages requires more resources). Default for pre-honeycomb devices (Android version 3.0) set to Classic, for post-honeycomb devices set to Advance. - Added display of the changelog
- Added language: Spanish
